r from its 2000's counterpart. Alot of the edges of buildings are alot smoother and a AI animations and textures run ALOT smoother. This provides the user with a more stable and smoother running game than sometimes before.Slight AI improvementI found this out while fighting certain enemies I could not exploit mechanics like I used to be able to. I saw that the AI had more flexablility than what it used to be. Now this does have a problem. The AI is still STUPID, military units still have that dumb short range of sight and wont hesitate to move if you destroy everything AROUND that circle of sight.What I likeSoo I touched on more bad things than I did good, dont get me wrong. I love this game it brings back alot of memories and what I touched on in my review is the differences that I saw ( or none there of). This game is still a really great and balanced RTS game even to this day. Its simplicity and yet it complex structure is what makes me always come back to it."
