76561197965657640,Recommended,266840,20924102,"Posted: 2 February, 2016",all,Raaj@SG,"If anyone has a black screen or the game does not load during startup on windows 10, you can follow the below steps to make it work.1) Goto your install dir (<drive> Steam\steamapps\common\Age of Mythology\Users)2) Open the Default.prf in Notepad and search for <windowmode>0</windowmode>3) Change this from 0 to 1. EG. <windowmode>1</windowmode>4) Save and launch game. This should do the trick untill developers fix the fullscreen issue."
