,Recommended,266840,28907436,Posted: 1 January,all,Carebear,If you are downloading this it most likely same reason most of us have. The most honoest review I can give is this is a double edged sword.What does this game give you?If you played the original back in the day the game allows you to go back and enjoy for what was a fantastic game. The game has been slightly upgraded visually but overall the core of this game is still there. All the campaign is playable and you able to play both titan and non titan edition.What it takes from you?If you loved this game in the past you may purchase this to a slight horror that it has not treated well by these new developers. First the game performs okay but can troubles depending on your CPU core setup. Second as you notice new dlc content has been added to the game which in fairness is OPTIONAL. However this is obivously a gimmick to make money and the DLC is poorly made and unbalanced and not taken any strategy or even looked at adding the meta of this game.This remaster is a double edged sword in terms of purchase. I recommend buying for those who want to re visit a great time in gaming but do not purchase the DLC. If this game is on sale I would say purchase for your collection.
